To reset your password, click the URL below.

<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>

<a href="http://localhost:3000/<%= @user.confirmation_token %>"> 
   http://localhost:3000/<%= @user.confirmation_token %>
</a>

If you did not request your password to be reset, 
just ignore this email and your password will continue to stay the same.

